              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-neutral-500">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></div>
                  Content marketing strategy
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></div>
                  Social media integration
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
