              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-neutral-400">Reviews</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-neutral-400">NAP Consistency</span>
